            <div id="primary-content">
              <a name="11617"></a><h1>About PRAS</h1>



<div class="banner"><img src="/media/global/wwwadminoxacuk/localsites/planningandresourceallocation/images/banners/Chess_horses.jpg" alt="&copy; Starcea Silviu  http://www.dreamstime.com/free-stock-image-chess-horses-rimagefree401372-resi990300
" height="135" width="470" class="floated"  /></div>

<p>The Planning and Resource Allocation Section forms part of the <a href="http://www.admin.ox.ac.uk/ac-div/">Academic Administration Division </a>within University Administration and Services, the University's central administration.</p>
<p>The principal responsibilities of the section are:</p>
<h3>Planning</h3>
<ul>
<li>Policy support to VC, Pro-VCs and Senior Officers</li>
<li>Liaising with the Higher Education Funding Council for England (HEFCE): policy, consultations, funding round</li>
<li>Student number planning and fee levels</li>
<li>Strategic Plan development and implementation (Divisional and service plans and budgets)</li>
<li>Support for Capital Planning processes</li>
<li>Secretariat for PRAC, Research Committee and sub-committees</li>
<li>Secretariat for Joint Resource Allocation Advisory Board, Joint Fees and Student Support Advisory Group, Joint Student Number Planning Sub-Committee</li>
</ul>
<h3>Resource Allocation</h3>
<ul>
<li>Modelling and operating the Joint Resource Allocation Methodology (JRAM)</li>
<li>Maintaining the Collegiate Funding Formula</li>
<li>Operating the 123 infrastructure charges</li>
</ul>
<h3>Data Management and Analysis</h3>
<ul>
<li>Regulatory funding returns</li>
<li>Research Excellence Framework submission</li>
<li>HEFCE/HESA Performance indicators and league table analysis</li>
<li>Manage access to HESA&rsquo;s Heidi online database</li>
</ul>
